# elev8.ai - APIs

This Document contains all the APIs that will be used in the development of Elev8.ai

## Auth [/]

### SIGN_IN [POST/signin]

+ Request (application/json)
        
            {
                "username": "sam",
                "password": "abc123"
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
                "message": "User Login Success",
                "token": "xyz"
            }
            
+ Response 401 (application/json)

            {
                "message": "Wrong Username or Password"
            }
        

### SIGN_UP [POST/signup]

+ Request (application/json)

            {
                "username": "sam",
                "email": "sam@test.com",
                "password": "abc123"
            }
        
+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
                "message": "User Created Successfully",
                "token": "xyz"
            }

### FORGOT_PASSWORD [POST/forgotpassword]

+ Request (application/json)

            {
                "email": "sam@test.com"
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
                "message": "OTP Generated and Sent
            }
            
+ Response 401 (application/json)

            {
                "message": "Invalid Email"
            }
            
### VALIDATE_OTP [POST/validateotp]

+ Request (application/json)

            {
                "otp": "85fds"
            }
            
+ Response 200 (application/json)   

            {
                "message": "OTP Validated"
            }
            
